nearEntities 
Game: ARMA 2  (1.00) 
Description: Find entities in the circle with given radius. If typeName(s) is (are) given 
, only entities of given type (or its subtype) are listed.  
Syntax:  
 position nearEntities radius or [typeName,radius] or [[typeName1,typeName2,...],radius] 
Parameters: 
position: Object or Array - 
[typeName,radius] or [[typeName1,typeName2,...],radius]: Array - 
Return Value: 
 Array